summary: Adds a new room to Breezehome with Mannequins, 20 Weapon Racks and a Smithy + More.
descriptionHtml:
I No longer support this mod, i can\'t keep up supporting all of them anymore, i have consolidated all my breezehome work into one mod, The Dovahkiin Hideout.

Please support that one instead, it has everything this one has and much more. Check out video below to see it running:

[youtube]-V1dmwNwibM[/youtube]
